99
00:08:06,397 --> 00:08:06,869
Check it out.

100
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:07,620
(I then)

101
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:10,738
(sent a court lady to the east wing
to check the cause of the noise.)

102
00:08:12,154 --> 00:08:13,660
(I have dismissed all
the guards in the East Palace)

103
00:08:14,274 --> 00:08:16,709
(to keep the banquet a secret.)

104
00:08:27,429 --> 00:08:28,500
(The snow showed that)

105
00:08:28,629 --> 00:08:30,629
(no one had approached
the east wing during this time.)

106
00:08:34,674 --> 00:08:35,790
(We rushed to the door to find)

107
00:08:35,850 --> 00:08:37,186
(the Wolve's envoy, Ada,)

108
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:38,790
(got crushed to death
by a heavy object.)

109
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,350
(The mysterious death of a visiting envoy)

110
00:08:41,474 --> 00:08:42,424
(is a matter of great importance.)

111
00:08:42,584 --> 00:08:44,544
"This case is weird. Please help me."

112
